rankheit zu diagnostizieren und zu behandeln</p></div><div class="flex items-start gap-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shield h-6 w-6 text-orange-startup flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"></path></svg><p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">Soziale Netzwerke und Messaging-Apps sind nicht die richtigen Orte, um Gesundheitsfragen zu besprechen</p></div></div><div class="bg-blue-vibrant/10 rounded-lg p-6 border border-blue-vibrant/20"><p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed font-medium">Und deshalb ist der beste Weg, die Bedürfnisse von Patienten und Gesundheitsdienstleistern zu erfüllen, sie zu befähigen, sich sicher miteinander zu verbinden und zu interagieren, mit entsprechendem Zugang zu Gesundheitsdaten.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-10"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-slate-dark">Menschen mit einer Mission</h2><div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-vibrant mx-auto"></div></div><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto"><div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-primary/10 to-blue-vibrant/10 rounded-2xl p-8"><div class="text-center mb-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-users h-16 w-16 text-teal-primary mx-auto mb-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><path d="M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744"></path><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></